						<span class="tech-name">React</span>
					</div>
					<div class="tech-item">
						<div class="tech-icon vue"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="148.28" height="128" viewBox="0 0 256 221"><path fill="#41B883" d="M204.8 0H256L128 220.8L0 0h97.92L128 51.2L157.44 0z"/><path fill="#41B883" d="m0 0l128 220.8L256 0h-51.2L128 132.48L50.56 0z"/><path fill="#35495E" d="M50.56 0L128 133.12L204.8 0h-47.36L128 51.2L97.92 0z"/></svg></div>
